{"tid":2385001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭受訪指對美國新政府感樂觀 冀公道對待香港","createTime":"2021-01-28T20:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T22:15:36.000Z","uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc772174e8557dbbc19299e915a0e27db51feeb","tid":2385001,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T20:54:05.000Z","msg":"香港特區行政長官林鄭月娥接受外國傳媒訪問時說，對美國新政府感到樂觀，希望會公道對待香港。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥接受CNBC訪問說，香港正經歷一個非常艱難時期，經常受全球關注。她承認美國總統的行政命令影響香港的企業以及她個人，相信新政府上場後，會對港區國安法有公正評價。<br />\n<br />\n被問及會否爭取連任，她沒正面回答，只說她是其中一位被安排做最困難工作的女性。"},{"pid":"776f7e5fbea573fdc6503e330ad92ffb7080bb9c","tid":2385001,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T21:36:38.000Z","msg":"愛登力？"},{"pid":"dfbe361349f55d1144845f948da2645fd10aeac2","tid":2385001,"uid":203305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T21:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jp7HE9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJp7HE9k.jpg&h=077ec497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放心林太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f34a3190272e39d12bf6bdf03e3023649f4936","tid":2385001,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:15:36.000Z","msg":"美國又唔係人治 7婆真樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}